query:
UPDATE permissions
                SET
                    edit_permissions = $2,
                    debug = $3,
                    ban_users = $4,
                    manage_leagues = $5,
                    manage_maps = $6,
                    manage_map_pools = $7,
                    manage_matchmaking_seasons = $8,
                    manage_matchmaking_times = $9,
                    manage_rally_point_servers = $10,
                    mass_delete_maps = $11,
                    moderate_chat_channels = $12,
                    manage_news = $13,
                    manage_bug_reports = $14,
                    manage_restricted_names = $15,
                    manage_signup_codes = $16
                WHERE user_id = $1
